      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MASHED POTATO (1) delivered a moderate run last time when fourth at this track over 305m behind Rose's Marie (18.55). Has claims if he runs up to expectations. PICK A CADILLAC (4) is still a maiden after 13 runs but rarely far away, the latest filling a minor placing when second at this track. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Leading chance. CADILLAC SNOOP (2) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish third (18.46) at this track in a Maiden over 305m. Likely to be in the finish again. BLACK STINGRAY (8) makes debut for the Tim Richards kennel. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Can feature with the right run.",
